Description:
    Create the base structure of the Angular.

Example:
    rails generate angular:init

    This will create:
        app/assets/javascripts/angular/YourApp.js.coffee
        app/assets/javascripts/angular/controllers.js.coffee
        app/assets/javascripts/angular/filters.js.coffee
        app/assets/javascripts/angular/services.js.coffee
        app/assets/javascripts/angular/directives.js.coffee
        app/assets/javascripts/angular/application_controller.js.coffee
